# LED Plant & Civil Marketing Website Stitch Scope
## 1. Product Overview
Marketing site for LED Plant and Civil whoe deliver dependable civil works, earthworks, underground service installations and plant hire solutions for developers and principal contractors across Southeast Queensland.
From early works right through to handover, we combine the right people, machinery and methods to keep projects safe, compliant and on program.
## 2. Platform Constraints
For web.

## 3. Stitch Project Context

- Existing Stitch redesign project: `projects/9514040008013092560`
- Design system source of truth: `.stitch/DESIGN.md`
